    "4.2); (c) validation features to check the quality and suitability of the generated prompts (Sect. 4.3); (d) an extension of the DSL's capabilities (Sect.",
    "3) in order to support these code generation and validation features, as well as introducing other capabilities, e.g., multi-language support; and (e) a case study of the use of Impromptu in a particular domain: building a prompt test-suite to evaluate generative AI systems (Sect. 5).The remainder of the paper is organized as follows.",
    "Section 2 discusses related work on prompt engineering and tool support.",
    "Then, Sect. 3 presents our DSL for prompt engineering and the toolkit that implements it.",
